news.title: Sweden's SBB creditors exchange debt for residential bonds in $158 million swap
news.para: SBB is at the centre of a Swedish property market bubble that began to unravel in 2022 when inflation and interest rates soared, triggering sharp cuts to its credit ratings and a plunge in its share price.

news.title: Government to reconstruct 28,643 dilapidated flats: Tamil Nadu CM
news.para: The Board currently maintains 1.94 lakh flats across Tamil Nadu and among them, 28,643 dwellings have been found to be dilapidated, the chief minister said.

news.title: New home sales in NCR increase by 6% in Q2 2024: Anarock
news.para: Not just this, NCR also saw a whopping 134% increase in new launches against Q1 2024, with approximately 17,030 units launched in Q2 2024.

news.title: State government asks Centre to grant approval for Bengaluru metro third phase
news.para: The State Government of Karnataka is actively pursuing approvals for two critical phases of the Bangalore Metro Rail project, urging the Central Government to expedite the process.

news.title: Mumbai: MMRDA to raise Rs 850-crore from KfW to develop urban infrastructure
news.para: The funds procured from KfW and MMRDA's resources will be primarily allocated towards various sustainable development projects within and around the Mumbai Metropolitan Region

news.title: Lucknow development body to commence land acquisition for four housing schemes
news.para: LDA chairperson and divisional commissioner Roshan Jacob approved the proposal for land acquisition for the projects during a meeting on Friday.

news.title: Karnataka government urges Centre to create GIFT City, fast-track approvals
news.para: In a statement by the minister's office, Kharge said that Karnataka wants to set up a Central Business District that will act as a global financial and IT hub.

news.title: Godrej Properties acquires leasehold rights for 11 acre land in Pune
news.para: The project has a developable potential of approximately 2.2 million sq ft with an estimated revenue potential of about Rs 1,800 crore.

news.title: Implement M-sand policy at the earliest: Uttar Pradesh CM
news.para: The CM has also asked the department to simplify the process of issuing licences. The process should be streamlined at the district level with a defined timeline.

news.title: Enforcement directorate attaches property worth Rs 31 crore of Shine City
news.para: The movable properties attached are in the form of luxury cars, jewellery, and cash worth Rs 1.42 crore. The immovable properties attached are in the form of two residential flats at Mumbai and Lucknow.

news.title: USA: Market for newly built homes slows as elevated mortgage rates put off many buyers
news.para: Last month's sales skidded to a seasonally adjusted annual rate of 619,000 units, the slowest pace since November, the U.S. Census Bureau reported Wednesday.

news.title: Saudi’s Dar Global plans to invest $300 million in USA
news.para: London-listed Dar Global hopes to announce its latest development in the United States before the year-end, said Ziad El Chaar, Dar Global's chief executive officer.

news.title: Cinven buys 70% stake in Spain’s Idealista for $3.10 billion
news.para: EQT bought a majority stake in Idealista from fund Apax Partners and the company's management in 2020 in a deal that valued the company at about 1.3 billion euros.

news.title: China's Sino Ocean receives winding-up petition
news.para: The petition was filed by the U.S. lender's London branch for non-repayment of 3.25% guaranteed notes due 2026 issued by a unit in an aggregate principal amount of $400 million.

news.title: Piramal Capital and Housing Finance receives Ba3 rating from Moody's
news.para: The rating agency said that Piramal Finance is driven by its high capitalization and an increasingly diversified portfolio mix, offset by its relatively low profitability, risks from its legacy real estate exposures and wholesale funding.

news.title: India Cement in talks with Bank of America & Nomura to raise Rs 500 crore
news.para: India Cements had mandated ICICI Bank and EY to arrange for the debt from lenders including private credit funds, as reported earlier and they have been in talks with lenders including private credit funds.

news.title: Apple set to lease office tower from Embassy Group in Bengaluru
news.para: This will be the US technology giant's latest addition to its corporate office footprint in India spanning Bengaluru, Mumbai, Hyderabad, and Gurugram.

news.title: Pune civic body cracks down on properties in green belt
news.para: Commercial establishments, including marriage halls, eateries, and other properties, were targeted during the drive conducted by the Pune Municipal Corporation (PMC).

news.title: Strike hits supply of crushed sand, civic works impacted in Pune
news.para: The move spells the growing impact of the Pune District Mining and Crusher Industries Association’s indefinite strike since June 22 on constructions being carried out by govt agencies and private construction firms.
